text.tspan: Read our xhain space rules in the wiki:
Read our workarea specific rules here:
Always put tools back to the specific place where
they belong. Ask if you're unsure. We don't bite :-)
Make sure the workbench is clear when you leave.
Tools belong on the tool board, equipment on the
shelves, trash in the rubbish bin.
If rubbish bins are full, please empty them in the back
yard (blue Furby will help you get there).
--> There is no rubbish service at xhain!
Do not use "green" electronics tools for other purposes.
(i.e. don't fix your bike with expensive eletronics pliers!)
